Speedbreaker had taken his attention away from Incinerator (dont know
why I did though :) and was not prepared. Two of the shells hit him in
the back, exploding with a loud blast of noise, and sent the Decepticon
falling towards Shockwave.

Beastbox on the other hand was glad that Incinerator had turned his
attention to Speedbreaker. He maneuvered himself towards the enemy now,
closing the gap between them. He fired again as he aproached.
